                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-202-off1132 t18301028-202-crimeloc1134"></join>, and am a <rs id="t18301028-202-viclabel1135" type="occupation">cheesemonger</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-202-victim1712 t18301028-202-viclabel1135"></join>. On the 29th of October this bacon hung by the door - I was told it was stolen; I had seen it two minutes before - I ran out, and took the prisoner with it, about two hundred yards from the shop; he threw himself down, and I gave him in charge.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301028-202-person1714">
                  JAMES 
                  WEST
               <interp inst="t18301028-202-person1714" type="surname" value="WEST"></interp>
